@NODE Intro "Introduction"

AMWAYDeck is a DataBase for use by AMWAY Distributors.

I designed it to keep track of my AMWAY customers, orders and stock.

Created with CanDo3.8® on an accelerated Amiga 1200 with 18 megs of RAM.

I hope it works OK on your system. Please let @{" me " LINK Address} know if it doesn't.

@ENDNODE
@NODE AMWAY "AMWAY"

   $$$$ Want to make some extra cash? $$$$
   Have some free time to yourself?
   Ever thought of having your own business?

   Then you might like to have a look at "AMWAY"

   It can offer a lot of opportunities.

   If you're interested, please let me know.

   They're even on the Internet at:

   http://www.amway.com/amway/globalv/australi.htm

To  be  in  AMWAY you first have to become a "Distributor" and in order to
become  a  "Distributor"  you  need a "Sponsor" If you would like me to be
your "Sponsor", please let me know at my @{" Address " LINK Address}.

